<html>
  <head>
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>A request to reset your password was received.  If you did not make this request you can ignore this email.  Your account has not been altered.</p>
    <p><%= link_to 'To reset your password follow this link', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>
    <p>If the link above does not work copy and paste the following address into a browser <%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>
    <p>The request will only be active for 12 hours. If you are unable to complete the process in that time you may make another request.</p>
  </body>
</html>
